text: tto yagob-i malhagileul adeuldeul a aegub-e deul-eogal ttae han mun-eulomandeul-eogaji malgo seolo daleun mun-eulo deul-eogala naega neohuileul wihae hana nim-eulobuteo amugeosdo yuyongke hal su eobs-euni sillo myeonglyeong-eun hananimkke man issnola geuleomeulo naneun geubun-e geman uijonhamyeo uitaghaneun modeunjadeul-i geubun-ege witaghadolog halila
